Male genitalia (
Figs. 11–13
): capsule 255–305 µm long, valva length 120–160 µm, aedeagus 220–275 µm long, cornutus 60–85 µm long.

Female genitalia (
Figs. 19–22
): total bursa length ca. 900 µm, signa 240–310 µm long, in some specimens very dissimilar, in others equally long. Anal papillae with ca. 9–10 setae, T 8 with some setae and scales. Ductus spermathecae with 2.5–3 convolutions.

